had a &s;on,</P>
<P>Sir <HI>John,</HI>&mdash;and three daughters,</P>
<P>1. <HI>Elizabeth,</HI> married to &s;ir William El|men.</P>
<P>2. <HI>Janet,</HI> married to &s;ir Thomas Lambert.</P>
<P>3. <HI>Maud,</HI> married to &s;ir William Ryther.</P>
<P>He died <HI>anno</HI> 1447, and was &s;ucceeded by
his &s;on,</P>
<P><PB N="205" REF="216">
XIII. Sir JOHN CONSTABLE of Hal&s;ham,
<HI>&amp;c.</HI><NOTE PLACE="marg">Mon. Ebor. Burton's coll. &amp;c.</NOTE> who was made a knight banneret by the
duke of Gloce&s;ter, <HI>anno</HI> 1448, and married
