and three daughters.</P>
<P>1. <HI>John,</HI> his heir.</P>
<P>2. Sir <HI>Ralph,</HI> who &s;ucceeded his brother.</P>
<P>3. <HI>William,</HI> who died without i&s;&s;ue.</P>
<P>1&s;t daughter, <HI>Marjory,</HI> married to Robert
