had three &s;ons, and three daughters.</P>
<P>1. <HI>John,</HI> who died before his father un|married.</P>
<P>2. <HI>Robert,</HI> who became his father's heir.</P>
<P>3. <HI>William,</HI> who &s;ucceeded his brother.</P>
<P>1&s;t daughter, <HI>Cecily,</HI> carried on the line
of this family, as will be &s;hown hereafter.</P>
<P>2. <HI>Catharine,</HI> married to John Moor, E&s;q;
