counterflowered, <HI>or;</HI> 2d and 3d <HI>argent,</HI> on a
fe&s;s <HI>gules,</HI> three cinque foils of the fir&s;t.</P>
<P>SUPPORTERS; two hor&s;es, <HI>argent.</HI></P>
<P>CREST; a cre&s;cent, <HI>gules.</HI></P>
