<DIV2 TYPE="peerage">
<HEAD>FORRESTER.</HEAD>
<P>Page 271. col. 2. line 48, <HI>add,</HI> and a daughter.</P>
<P><PB N="714" REF="747">
<HI>Mariotte Forre&s;ter,</HI> married to Sir James Sandi|lands
of Calder.</P>
<P>Page 272. after line 9. <HI>add,</HI> He had al&s;o a
daughter,</P>
<P><HI>Elizabeth,</HI> married to Mr. David MacGill of
